\id 1PE - Zanaki 1 Peter 
\h 1 Petero 
\toc3 1 Petero 
\toc2 1 Petero 
\toc1 Enyaarubha yo okutaanga ya Petero 
\mt2 Enyaarubha yo okutaanga ya 
\mt1 Petero 
\imt1 Obhutaangiro 
\ip Petero akabhakaamira abhiikirirya bhoosi bhano bhakwiikara kya abhagini kwe ekigirirye bhaari bhanyarageeni mubhyaaro bhyaaru. Petero akakaama enyaarubha yino hano yaari mumugye gwa Rooma, ahagiro hano yabhirikiiri Babeeri kwe ekigirirye haari omugye gwo obhubhi bhwaaru. 
\ip Petero akakaama enyaarubha yino ku Bhakrisito bhano bhaari bharanyaaka iguru wo obhwiikirirya bhwaabhu. Akabhahiitya kubha Yeesu akanyaaka no okukorwa bhubhi, na Abhakrisito bhiisigire okukorerwa ego. Akabhamenyeekererya kubha bharatura okwiimeerera bhugumiru kutuukana no orubhaango rwa Taatabhugya, na bhiikongʼeererye kwiibhaga rye enyaako, kwo okubha Taatabhugya arakorera eziinyaako zino kubhakora abhaatu bhano bhabhone orubhaango. 
\c 1  
\s1 Obhukeerya 
\p  
\v 1 Enyaarubha yino nikaamiri enye Petero, omweega wa Yeesu Krisito. Ndabhakaamira emwe bhano musorirwe na Taatabhugya, bhano mukunyaragana no okwiikara kya abhagini mubhyaaro bhya Poonto, Garatia, Kapadokia, Asia na Bitinia.  
\v 2 Kweema ekare, Taata Taatabhugya akabhamenya no okubhasora kwiiguru waaye. Ekoro waaye akabhakora mubhe abhahoreeru, okubha mumwiigwe Yeesu Krisito no okweeribhwa na amanyiinga gaaye.\f + \fr 1:2 \fk Okubha mumwiigwe Yeesu Krisito no okweeribhwa na amanyiinga gaaye \ft ku Kiyunaani ni \fqa kwo okwiituruurirwa amanyiinga gaaye. \ft Kuriingʼaana na \xt Okurwa 24:3-8, \ft Abhiiziraeri bhaari bhariituruurirwa amanyiinga ge engʼoombe okweerekya kubha bhariigwa eriiragano ryaabhu na Taatabhugya. Petero arabhuga kubha, amanyiinga ga Yeesu ni rubhaaso rwe eriiragano eriihya gati wa Taatabhugya na abhaatu bhaaye. \xt Rora Abheeburania 9:18-21.\f* 
\p Orubhaango no omureembe mwaaru bhibhe neemwe. 
\s1 Obhwiikirirya bhweetu 
\p  
\v 3 Tumukumye Taatabhugya, Taata wo Omukuru weetu Yeesu Krisito. Kwe ebhigoongi bhyaaye bhyaaru, akatwiibhura kabhiri kwe enzira yo okumuryoora Yeesu Krisito okurwa mubhaku. Kweego, tubhweeni eriisigo ryo obhuhoru.  
\v 4 Bhoono etwe twoosi turaganya okugabha orubhaango runo Taatabhugya abhiikiri mwiisaaro, kwiiguru wa abhaatu bhaaye. Orubhaango ruyo rutakutura kubhora, kusarika, naabhe kunyaara.  
\v 5 Taatabhugya arabhariibha emwe kwe eziinguru zyaaye, kwo okubha muramwiikirirya Yeesu Krisito. Arageenderera okubhariibha tee orubhaango rwo obhutuurya ruraarorekane kwe eziisiku zyo obhuteero. 
\p  
\v 6 Ambe, muzomererwe bhukongʼu kumangʼana gayo, yiingabha bhoono kwe eriibhaga iguhi murabha ne ebhigoongi iguru yo obhusakya bhwa tuubho nzaru.  
\v 7 Naabhe ezahaabu ni kigiro kino kikusakibhwa kwo okwookibhwa mumuriro, naabhe erasarika. Egoego obhwiikirirya bhweenyu, bhuno obhuguri bhukuru kukira ezahaabu, bhurareengibhwa no obhusakya, no okurorekana kubha nibhwo obhweene. Kweego, Yeesu Krisito orusiku runo araaze okwiiyeerekya mwaasi, arabhaha omukumo, obhuguungo no obhusuuku.  
\v 8 Emwe mukyaari kumurora, nawe muramuseega. Kweeki yiingabha mutakumurora bhoono, nawe muramwiikirirya. Kweego, munabhwo obhuzomererwa bhukuru bhwo obhuguungo, bhuno bhutakuhaywa,  
\v 9 kwo okubha, murasuungʼaana obhutuurya bhweenyu. Obhutuurya bhuyo nibhwo obhureengererya bhwo obhwiikirirya bhweenyu. 
\p  
\v 10 Abharooti bhe ekare bhakakora omukya okumenya obhutuurya bhuyo, nabho bhakaroota kwiiguru yo orubhaango rwa Taatabhugya runo rubhahikiiri emwe.  
\v 11 Ekoro wa Krisito yaari muusi waabhu, akaroota kubha Krisito aranyaakibhwa, no okuhita enyaako yiyo, arabhona obhuguungo. Abharooti bhayo bhakakomya bhukongʼu bhamenye kubha, amangʼana gayo garabha ryoori, na garamubhonabhwi.  
\v 12 Taatabhugya akabhakuundukurira abharooti bhayo kubha, amangʼana gano bhaari bharootiri, gataabhatunirye ebho abheene, nawe emwe. Amangʼana gano bhaagaambiri, nigo mukarwaazirwa na bhano bhaabhareeteeri Amangʼana Amazomu iguru wa Yeesu Krisito. Nabho bhakabhakeerenerya Amangʼana gayo Amazomu kwo obhunagya bhwe Ekoro Muhoreeru wuno yatumirwe okurwa mwiisaaro. Amangʼana gayo, naabhe bhamaraika\f + \fr 1:12 \fk Bhamaraika\ft . Rora engʼana \ft \+it maraika\+it* mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* bhariigoomba bhukongʼu okugamenya. 
\s1 Okwiikara kya abhaana bha Taatabhugya 
\p  
\v 13 Kweego, mwiibhanure bhuzomu kwo okuteengeeza no okubha na kusuuhu. Mutuure eriisigo ryoosi murubhaango runo muraasuungʼaane hano Yeesu Krisito araaze okwiiyeerekya mwaasi.  
\v 14 Emwe ni bhaana bha Taatabhugya. Ambe bhoono, mumwiigwe, mutiikirirya okutuniirira kweeki eziinaamba zino mwaari nazyo, hano mwaari mukyaari kumumenya Yeesu Krisito.  
\v 15 Taatabhugya wuno yabhabhirikiiri, ni muhoreeru. Bhoono emwe kweeki mureenderwa mubhe abhahoreeru muteemwa yeenyu yoosi,  
\v 16 kwo obhugazuro Taatabhugya abhugiri mu Makaamo Amahoreeru, “Mubhe abhahoreeru, kwo okubha enye ni muhoreeru.”\f + \fr 1:16 \xt Rora Abharaawi 11:44-45, 19:2, 20:7.\f* 
\p  
\v 17 Taatabhugya atakuhiingirirya omuutu wowoosi. Arabhatinira ekiina abhaatu bhoosi kuriingʼaana na amahokya gano bhakoriri. Emwe muramubhirikira Taata, kweego mwiikare kwo okumwiigwa Taatabhugya mwiibhaga rino risaagiri, ryo okwiikara kya abhagini mukyaaro hano.  
\v 18 Emwe, mwaari muriikara kuriingʼaana ne eziiteemwa zino zitaari no obhugazuro, kyeego mukagabha okurwa kubhazaazi bheenyu. Bhoono mumenye kubha, Taatabhugya ataabhatuurirye emwe okurwa muteemwa yiyo kwo okuriha ebhigiro bhino bhikusarika, kye eziimbirya ne ezahaabu.  
\v 19 Nawe, akabhatuurya kwe enzira ya amanyiinga gano gano obhuguri bhukuru, kweeki amanyiinga ge engʼoondu\f + \fr 1:19 \fk Engʼoondu\ft . Rora engʼana yino mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* gano gatana obhurema naabhe ibhati. Amanyiinga gayo nigo ga Krisito.  
\v 20 Kweema ekyaaro kikyaari kubhuumbwa, Taatabhugya yaari amariri okumusora kwe ekigirirye kiyo. Nawe akaganya tee eziisiku zino zyo obhuteero, niho akamureeta no okumweerekya mwaasi kubhaatu bhoosi mukyaaro. Gayo goosi yakoriri kwiiguru weenyu.  
\v 21 Kuhitira ku Krisito, muramwiikirirya Taatabhugya. Ewe yamuryooriri no okumuha obhuguungo na kiyo nikyo kikukora emwe muramwiikirirya no okumwiisiga Taatabhugya. 
\p  
\v 22 Emwe muriikara kuriingʼaana na ameegyo ge eheene iguru wa Yeesu. Kweego, mweeriibhwe na bhoono muranagya okuseega abharikyeenyu eheene. Ambe, mwiiseege kwe ekoro yoosi na kwe ekoro nzomu,  
\v 23 kwo okubha mwiibhwiirwe kabhiri. Okwiibhurwa kuyo, kutakutuukana na bhawuuso weenyu, ebho bharakwa, nawe mwiibhwiirwe kwe engʼana ya Taatabhugya yino ekuruusya obhuhoru na eragumira tee kirakeego.  
\v 24 Kyeego Amakaamo Amahoreeru gakubhuga, 
\q1 “Abhaatu bhoosi ni kya amatu, 
\q1 no obhuzomu bhwaku ni kye ebhibharyo bhino bhikwiimerya. 
\q1 Amatu garanyaara ne ebhibharyo bhiragwa, 
\q1  
\v 25 nawe engʼana yo Omukuru eragumira kirakeego.”\f + \fr 1:25 \xt Rora Isaya 40:6-8.\f* 
\m Engʼana yiyo niyo Amangʼana Amazomu gano mukarwaazirwa. 
\c 2  
\p  
\v 1 Ambe, mutige ebhibhi bhyoosi, obhungʼeenererya bhwe eziituubho zyoosi, orurimi no omugono, naabhe mutamoonya naabhe kusuuhu.  
\v 2-3 Bhoono mumariri kungʼura kubha Omukuru Yeesu ni muzomu.\f + \fr 2:2-3 \xt Rora Zaburi 34:8.\f* Ambe, kyeego abhaana abharere bhano bhakweenda amabheere ga nina waabhu, emwe mubhe ne enyoota ya amabheere amazomu ge engʼana ya Taatabhugya, gano mukunywa, muranagya okukura no okumumenya Taatabhugya kimwe. 
\s1 Abhaatu abhasorwa bha Taatabhugya Muhoreeru 
\p  
\v 4 Yeesu niwe eriigina eriihoru ryo okwoombokera. Eriigina riyo, abhaatu bhakaryaanga, nawe Taatabhugya akarisora, kweeki rino obhuguri bhukuru mumeeso gaaye. Ambe, mukumwiisukira Yeesu,  
\v 5 murabha kya amagina go obhuhoru, mwoombokwe no okubha eriikiindaasi rye ekoro. Kweeki murabha abhaseengeri abhahoreeru bhano musorirwe okumuruusirya Taatabhugya ebhimweeso bhye ekoro, bhino bhikumuzomera kwe enzira ya Yeesu Krisito.  
\v 6 Kyeego Amakaamo Amahoreeru gakubhuga, 
\q1 “Murore, mumugye gwa Sayuni\f + \fr 2:6a \fk Sayuni \ft ni eriina eriindi ku \fqa Yerusaremu, \ft omugye guno eriiseengerero rya Taatabhugya rikoombokwa.\f* niratuura eriigina eriikuru ryo obhurusa, 
\q1 kweeki niryo eriigina ryo obhuguri obhukuru rino niasoriri. 
\q1 Na wowoosi wuno akumwiikirirya Yeesu Krisito kubha niwe eriigina riyo, 
\q1 atakusuukibhwa na rumwe!”\f + \fr 2:6b \xt Rora Isaya 28:16.\f* 
\m  
\v 7 Kweemwe bhano mukwiikirirya eriigina riyo, ni ryo obhuguri obhukuru. Nawe, kwiiguru ya bhano bhatakuriikirirya, Amakaamo Amahoreeru garabhuga iguru waabhu, 
\q1 “Eriigina rino abhoomboki bhaaryaangiri, 
\q1 niryo ribheeri eriigina eriikuru ryo obhurusa.”\f + \fr 2:7 \xt Rora Zaburi 118:22.\f* 
\m  
\v 8 Kweeki, Amakaamo Amahoreeru garabhuga, 
\q1 “Eriigina riyo niryo rino abhaatu bhakwiikuzaku, 
\q1 na riragirirya abhaatu bhabhe bharagwa.”\f + \fr 2:8 \xt Rora Isaya 8:14.\f* 
\m Abhaatu bharagwa, kwo okubha bhatakwiigwa engʼana ya Taatabhugya. Ego niigo bhaari bhatuuriirwe kweema ekare. 
\p  
\v 9 Nawe emwe ni kisyooko ekisorwa, abhaseengeri bho Omutemi, abhaatu bhaaye abhahoreeru, abhaatu bha Taatabhugya omweene, okubha muraarike amahokya amakuru ga Taatabhugya. Ewe akabhabhirikira okurwa mukiirima, akabhasikirya mubhweero bhwaaye obhukuru bhwo okuruguurya.\f + \fr 2:9 \xt Rora Okurwa 19:6; Isaya 43:20-21.\f* 
\v 10 Eziisiku zino zyahitiri mutaari bhaatu bha Taatabhugya, nawe bhoono emwe ni bhaatu bhaaye. Kweeki mutaari mwaabhiirwe na Taatabhugya, nawe bhoono, mwaabhiirwe.\f + \fr 2:10 \xt Rora Hosea 2:23.\f* 
\s1 Okwiikara mukyaaro kyeego abhaatu bha Taatabhugya 
\p  
\v 11 Abhaseegwa bhaane, emwe ni bhagini na abhahiti mukyaaro kino. Kweego, nirabhiisasaama kubha, mutiikirirya eziinaamba zyeenyu eziimbiihu, zino zikuhakana neemwe, zibhahize.  
\v 12 Mubhe ne eteemwa nzomu gati wa abhaatu bhano bhatamumenyiri Taatabhugya, okubha kyeego bhakubhiitaamirirya kubha, murakora obhubhi, bharore amahokya geenyu amazomu. Niho bhakunagya okumukumya Taatabhugya kwiiguru weenyu, kurusiku rwo okuuza kwaaye. 
\p  
\v 13 Mubhe murasuuka abhakaangati bha abhaatu, kwiiguru yo okumusuuka Omukuru Yeesu. Musuuke omutemi weenyu, kwo okubha ewe niwe omukaangati omukuru mukyaaro kyeenyu.  
\v 14 Kweeki musuuke abhakaangati bhe emigye, abheene bhakasorwa no omukaangati wuyo. Bhakasorwa okubha bhabhe bharatuura obhutemwa bhwa abhaatu bhano bhakukora obhubhi, no okukumya bhano bhakukora amangʼana amazomu.  
\v 15 Obhuseegi bhwa Taatabhugya ni kubha, mukore amangʼana amazomu, okubha mukirye abhageege bhano bhatamenyiri amangʼana gaaye. 
\p  
\v 16 Mwiikare kwo obhwiiragaanzi, nawe mutakorera obhwiiragaanzi bhuyo okubhisa amabhi. Mwiikare kyeego abhagya bha Taatabhugya bhakweenderwa kwiikara.  
\v 17 Mubhasuuke abhaatu bhoosi, na museege abhiikirirya abharikyeenyu. Mumwiigwe Taatabhugya, na mumusuuke omutemi weenyu. 
\s1 Amaragiriryo kubhagya 
\p  
\v 18 Emwe abhagya, mubhasuuke bhukongʼu abhakuru bheenyu kwo obhusuuku bhwoosi, bhabhe ni bhazomu na abhanyoohu, kasi bhahaari.  
\v 19 Mwiikongʼeererye eziinyaako zino zitakweenderwa, kwiiguru yo okumusuuka Taatabhugya, hayo muramuzomera.  
\v 20 Kyeego muriikongʼeererya eziinyaako zino mukweenderwa kwe ekigirirye kyo obhubhi bhweenyu, bhutariho obhweera. Nawe eraabhe muriikongʼeererya eziinyaako kwiiguru yo okukora amazomu, hayo muramuzomera Taatabhugya. 
\p  
\v 21 Mureenderwa mwiikongʼeererye ego, kwo okubha Krisito omweene akanyaakibhwa kwiiguru weenyu. Kwo okukora ego, akabhatigira ekireengyo, okubha mubhe muramweega.  
\v 22 Ewe ataakoriri ebhibhi bhiyo bhyoosi, naabhe okugaamba orurimi ruyo rwoosi.\f + \fr 2:22 \xt Rora Isaya 53:9.\f* 
\v 23 Hano yatukirwe, ataakyooriri engʼana yiyo yoosi. Hano yanyaakiibhwe, ataabharekirye abhanyaakya kubha, arabharihira ekisiiyoomba. Nawe, akamutigira Taatabhugya goosi, atine ekiina kwe eheene.  
\v 24 Krisito omweene akagega ebhibhi bhyeetu kumubhiri gwaaye, akanyaakibhwa kumusaraba. Akakora ego, okubha etwe tutabhaahwa kweeki ne ebhibhi, nawe twiikare obhwiikari bhuno bhukweenderwa embere wa Taatabhugya. Emwe muhonirwe kwo okuhitira okutemwa kwaaye.  
\v 25 Mwaari kye eziingʼoondu zino zikubhura, nawe bhoono, mumukyooreeri ewe omuriisya weenyu wuno akubhariibha. 
\c 3  
\s1 Amaragiriryo kubhasubhe na abhakari 
\p  
\v 1-2 Kweego emwe abhakari, mubhiigwe abhasubhe bheenyu, okubha eraabhe bhariho bhano bhatakutuniirira ameegyo ga Taatabhugya, bharore eziiteemwa zyeenyu eziinzomu na bharutwe nabho. Kweego bharanagya okumwiikirirya Taatabhugya kutama kubhuurirwa ngʼana.  
\v 3 Mutabha abhaatu bho okwiizomya kwiigutu ego, kyaabhurya okusuka eziinzweeri, okwiibhoha ebhigiro bhye ezahaabu kasi emyeenda gyo obhuguri bhukuru.  
\v 4 Nawe obhuzomu bhweenyu bhutaangire muziikoro, bhuno bhutakunagya kusarika naabhe okukuunguha. Obhuzomu bhuyo, ni kubha ne ekoro nzomu no obhunyoohu, na nibhwo obhuzomu bhuno bhuno obhuguri obhukuru mumeeso ga Taatabhugya.  
\v 5 Ego niigo ekare hayo abhakari abhahoreeru bhano bhaamwiisigiri Taatabhugya, bhahiizomya kwo okubhiigwa abhasubhe bhaabhu.  
\v 6 Owumwe waabhu yaari ni Saara, omukari wa Aburahamu.\f + \fr 3:6 \fk Aburahamu\ft . Rora engʼana yino mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* Ewe yaari aramwiigwa omusubhe waaye bhuzomu, akumubhirikira omukuru waaye. Egoego emwe kweeki, eraabhe murakora amazomu kutama okwoobhoha riyo ryoosi, ambe mubheeri abhaana bhaaye. 
\p  
\v 7 Neemwe abhasubhe, mwiikare na abhakari bheenyu kwa amangʼeeni, mukumenya kubha bhatana amanaga kyeego emwe. Mubhatuge kwo okubhasuuka, kwe ekigirirye ebho bhoosi bharagabha orubhaango rwo obhuhoru. Kweego abhasubhe, mukore ego, okubha amasabhi geenyu gataribhirwa. 
\s1 Okunyaaka kwe ekigirirye kyo okukora amazomu 
\p  
\v 8 Mubhuteero, nirabhabhuurira mwoosi kubha, mubhe na amiiseego gamwe, mugwaatane, museegane kya abhahiiri, murorerane ebhigoongi, na mubhe bhanyoohu.  
\v 9 Mutariha amabhi kwa amabhi, kasi ituki kwi ituki, nawe mubhatweere ebhite. Taatabhugya abhabhirikiiri okukora ego, na arabhatweera ebhite kwo okukora gayo.  
\v 10 Kyeego Amakaamo Amahoreeru gakubhuga, 
\q1 “Omuutu akweenda kwiikara bhuzomu no okubha no obhuzoma, 
\q1 atige okumoonya no okungʼeenererya. 
\q1  
\v 11 Na atige okukora amabhi, akore amazomu. 
\q1 Kweeki akore omukya okwiikara kwo omureembe na abharikyaaye, 
\q1  
\v 12 kwo okubha Omukuru, Taatabhugya arabhatuga bhano bhakukora eheene, 
\q1 na ariigwa amasabhi gaabhu. 
\q1 Nawe, bhano bhakukora amabhi, arabhaanga eziisiku zyoosi.”\f + \fr 3:12 \xt Rora Zaburi 34:12-16.\f* 
\m  
\v 13 Weewi arabhakorera amabhi, eraabhe murakora amazomu kwo omukya eriibhaga ryoosi?  
\v 14 Naabhe ego, eraabhe muranyaaka kwo okukora eheene, Taatabhugya arabhatweera ebhite. Kweego, mutatuurirwa obhuhoobhi naabhe okwoobhoha bhano bhakubhanyaakya. Nawe mumukore Krisito abhe Omukuru omweene muziikoro zyeenyu.  
\v 15 Mwiibhanure eriibhaga ryoosi okumukyoora wowoosi wuno akubhabhuurya kino mukwiisiga. Mukore ego kwo obhunyoohu no obhusuuku,  
\v 16 muraabhe no omutima mweero, okubha eraabhe bharabhiitaamirirya kwa amangʼana amazomu gano mukukora iguru wa Krisito, ambe bharore eziisoni.  
\v 17 Hakiriku okunyaaka kwe ekigirirye kyo okukora amazomu, eraabhe ni miiseego ga Taatabhugya, kukira okunyaaka kwo okukora amabhi. 
\p  
\v 18 Niigo ego, kwo okubha Krisito omweene akanyaakibhwa, kwe ekigirirye kye ebhibhi bhya abhaatu, yiingabha ewe ataari ne ebhibhi. Akakwa rugeendo rumwe ego ne ekiisa, okubha atwiigwaanie na Taatabhugya. Akiitwa omubhiri, nawe kwo obhuturo bhwe Ekoro Muhoreeru\f + \fr 3:18 \fk Ekoro Muhoreeru\ft . Rora amangʼana gano mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* akabhona kweeki obhuhoru.  
\v 19 Kwe enzira ye Ekoro wuyo, akagya okurwaazira abhaatu bhano bhaakuuri, na bhoono eziikoro zyaabhu zibhohirwe.  
\v 20 Eziikoro ziyo ni zya bhano bhataamwiigwiiri Taatabhugya ekare hayo, hano Nuhu yaari akukora emeeri. Taatabhugya akiikongʼeererya ebhibhi bhyaabhu tee emeeri hano yakorirwe, nawe mubhuteero abhaatu bhanaane abheene ego, nibho bhano bhakatuuribhwa kwe enzira ya amaanzi.\f + \fr 3:20 \xt Rora Obhweemero 6.\f* 
\v 21 Amaanzi gayo ni kireengyo kyo obhubatiizo, bhuno bhukubhatuurya, bhutari kwo okuruusyaho eriikwe mumubhiri, nawe ni kwo okumusabha Taatabhugya abhahe omutima omweero. Amangʼana gayo, garaturikana kwo okuhitira okuryooka kwa Yeesu Krisito.  
\v 22 Ewe akagya mwiisaaro, na bhoono yiikeeri orubhaara rwo obhuryo rwa Taatabhugya. Arakaangata bhamaraika ne ebhigiro bhyoosi bhino bhikubhaaha na bhyo obhunagya. 
\c 4  
\s1 Obhwiikari bhuno bhukumuzomera Taatabhugya 
\p  
\v 1 Ambe, kyaabhurya Krisito akanyaaka kumubhiri gwaaye, emwe kweeki mubhe mwiibhanwiiri mumiiseego geenyu okunyaaka kyeego ewe yanyaakiri. Niragaamba ego, kwo okubha, omuutu wuno amariri kunyaaka kumubhiri gwaaye, atakubhaahwa kweeki ne ebhibhi.  
\v 2 Kwe enzira yiyo, obhwiikari bhwaaye bhwoosi bhuno bhusaagiri, ariikara kuriingʼaana na kyeego Taatabhugya akuseega, etari kwe eziinaamba zya abhaatu.  
\v 3 Muziisiku zino zihitiri, mwaari murakora amangʼana ga abhaatu bhano bhatamumenyiri Taatabhugya. Mukatuniirira eziinaamba zyeenyu eziimbiihu zyo okuseega abhakari naabhe abhasubhe bhaaru. Kweeki mukaseega obhunywi obhuraara, obhusoohu, no okuseengera emisaambwa gyo okubhaazwa, gino gyaangirwe na Taatabhugya. Mwaari murakora amangʼana gayo kwe eriibhaga rino riisiri. Bhoono gabheere hayo.  
\v 4 Bhoono, abhaatu bhano bhatamumenyiri Taatabhugya, bhararuguura hano bhakurora kubha mutakwiisaangya nabho naabhe hasuuhu okukora amabhi gano gahitireenie, kweego, bharabhatuka.  
\v 5 Nawe, abheene bhareenderwa okwiisasaama embere wo Omukuru Yeesu wuno yiibhanwiiri okutinira ekiina abhaatu bhoosi, abhahoru na abhaku.  
\v 6 Kiyo nikyo ekigirirye kya abhaatu bhano bhaakuuri, bhaarwaaziirwe Amangʼana Amazomu bhakubha bhakyaari bhahoru, okubha yiingabha bharatinirwa ekiina mubhwiikari bhwaabhu kya abhaandi, bhiikare kwo obhuturo bhwe Ekoro Muhoreeru, kyeego Taatabhugya ari muhoru. 
\p  
\v 7 Obhuteero bhwa amangʼana goosi bhuhikiri. Kweego, mubhe na kusuuhu no okwiiriiha kwa amiiseego go obhweera, okubha munagye okusabha.  
\v 8 Kukira gayo goosi, mwiiseege bhukongʼu, kwo okubha obhuseegi bhuraabhira ebhibhi bhyaaru.\f + \fr 4:8 \xt Rora Eziimetari 10:12.\f* 
\v 9 Mubhe abhaatu bho okuginihya abharikyeenyu kutama kwiiririirira. 
\p  
\v 10 Bhoosi bhaheerwe obhuturo okurwa ku Taatabhugya, okubha bhasakirye abhaandi. Bhareenderwa kubhikorera bhuzomu, kyeego abhiimeerereri abhazomu bho orubhaango rwa Taatabhugya.  
\v 11 Eraabhe omuutu aheerwe amangʼana go okugaamba, agaambe kyeego gakurwa ku Taatabhugya. Na kyeego omuutu aheerwe obhunagya okubhahokeerya abharikyaaye, ahokye kwo obhunagya bhuno bhukurwa ku Taatabhugya. Kwe enzira yiyo, Taatabhugya araguungibhwa kuhitira Yeesu Krisito mumangʼana goosi. Ewe omweene ano obhuguungo no obhunagya bhwa kirakeego na kirakeego. Gabhe ego. 
\s1 Okunyaaka kwiiguru wa Yeesu 
\p  
\v 12 Abhaseegwa bhaane, mutaruguura iguru ye enyaako haari yino ekubhabhona gati weenyu okusakya obhwiikirirya bhweenyu. Mutarora ni kye ekigiro ekigini kino kikubhabhona.  
\v 13 Nawe muzomererwe kubha, muranyaaka kyeego Krisito yanyaakiri. Muzomererwe bhoono, okubha mubhe no obhuzomererwa reke, hano araaze okweerekya obhuguungo bhwaaye.  
\v 14 Eraabhe muratukwa kwe ekigirirye kye eriina rya Krisito, mumenye kubha muratweerwa ebhite. Eriingʼana riyo rireerekya kubha Ekoro wa Taatabhugya wo obhuguungo ari hamwe neemwe.  
\v 15 Ambe, omuutu ataaza kubhona enyaako kwe ekigirirye kyo obhwiiti, obhwiibhi, okukora amabhi kasi okwiisikirya mumangʼana ga abhaandi.  
\v 16 Nawe wuyo woosi wuno araanyaakibhwe kwo okubha Omukrisito, atarora soni. Nawe amukumye Taatabhugya, abhirikiirwe kwe eriina riyo.  
\v 17 Mumenye kubha, eriibhaga ryo okutina ekiina rihikiri, na Taatabhugya arataanga kwo okubhatinira ekiina abhaatu bhaaye. Bhoono eraabhe okutina ekiina kurataangira kweetwe abhaatu bhaaye abheene, erabhabhwi kubhano bhakwaanga Amangʼana Amazomu ga Taatabhugya?  
\v 18 Amakaamo Amahoreeru garabhuga, 
\q1 “Eraabhe ni kukongʼu ku bhe eheene okutuuribhwa, 
\q1 erabhabhwi ku bhe ebhibhi bhano bhatakumuseengera Taatabhugya?”\f + \fr 4:18 \xt Rora Eziimetari 11:31.\f* 
\m  
\v 19 Kweego, bhano bhakunyaakibhwa mumiiseego ga Taatabhugya, bhiituure kwo Omubhuumbi omuheene wuyo, bhageenderere kukora amazomu. 
\c 5  
\s1 Okuriibha abhaatu bha Taatabhugya 
\p  
\v 1 Bhoono niragaamba neemwe abhakaruka bhe ekanisa. Enye ni mukaruka omurikyeenyu, niruuzi kwa meeso gaane kyeego Krisito yanyaakiibhwe. Kweeki, ndiigwaatania mubhuguungo bhuno bhuraarorekane. Kweego nirabhiisasaama emwe,  
\v 2 mubhe abhariisya abhazomu bhe ekanisa yino mukahaabhwa na Taatabhugya. Kweeki muyiriibhe kwe ekoro nzomu, nawe etari kwo okuhatikwa. Mutakora emirimo gyeenyu kwe enaamba ye eziimbirya, nawe kwe ekoro yo omukya.  
\v 3 Mutabha abhariisya abhabhaandirirya kubhano muheerwe okubhakaangata, nawe obhwiikari bhweenyu bhubhe ekireengyo kizomu kweebho.  
\v 4 Yeesu Krisito niwe Omuriisya Omukuru we ekanisa, hano araarorekane kubhweero, murasaambirwa esaambo yo obhuguungo bhuno bhutana obhuteero. 
\p  
\v 5 Egoego neemwe abhamura, mubhasuuke abhakaruka. Neemwe mwoosi mureenderwa kubha abhanyoohu na bho okusakirania na abharikyeenyu. Mukore ego, kwo okubha Amakaamo Amahoreeru garabhuga, 
\q1 “Taatabhugya ahaabhaanga bhano bhakwiigega, 
\q1 nawe, ahaabhaha abhanyoohu orubhaango.”\f + \fr 5:5 \xt Rora Eziimetari 3:34.\f* 
\m  
\v 6 Ambe, mubhe muriiyiikya iyaasi wo obhunagya bhwa Taatabhugya, neewe arabhatiirya eriibhaga ryaaye hano riraahike.  
\v 7 Mumutigire Taatabhugya eziinyaako zyeenyu zyoosi, kwo okubha ewe arabhatuga. 
\s1 Okumwaanga Seetaani kwo okumwiikirirya Taatabhugya 
\p  
\v 8 Muteengeeze, na mubhe meeso eriibhaga ryoosi, kwo okubha omubhisa weenyu, Seetaani,\f + \fr 5:8 \fk Seetaani\ft . Rora engʼana yino mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* arageendageenda kyeego endwi yino ekuruma, erageendageenda ekomye omuutu, emurye.  
\v 9 Ambe, mumwaange Seetaani, mwiimeerere tiri kwo okumwiikirirya Taatabhugya. Mumenye kubha, abhiikirirya abharikyeenyu mukyaaro hoosi, bharanyaakibhwa kyeego emwe. 
\p  
\v 10 Taatabhugya arabhaha orubhaango rwoosi! Akabhabhirikira emwe, okubha mugwaatane neewe mubhuguungo bhwaaye bhwa kirakeego, hamwe na Krisito. Hano mukunyaaka kwiibhaga iguhi, nawe ewe omweene arabhagumirya, arabhaha eziinguru no okubhamenyeekererya.  
\v 11 Taatabhugya abhaahe kirakeego! Gabhe ego. 
\s1 Amangʼana go okuraga 
\p  
\v 12 Nibhakaamiiri enyaarubha enguhi yino, kwo obhusakirya bhwa Sirwano.\f + \fr 5:12 \fk Sirwano \ft arabhirikirwa \fqa Siira \ft mukitabhu kya Amahokya ga Abheega.\f* Enye nimumenyiri bhuzomu, kubha ni muheene. Amiiseego gaane ni kubhatoongera ekoro no okubheerekya, amangʼana gano ni rubhaango rwe eheene rwa Taatabhugya. Kutuukana no orubhaango ruyo, mwiimeerere tiri!  
\v 13 Abhiikirirya bhe ekanisa yino eri Babeeri,\f + \fr 5:13 \fk Babeeri \ft ni riina rino abhaatu abhaandi bhaari bhararihokeerya okutiga okutogora omugye gwa Rooma.\f* abhasorwa abharikyeenyu, bharabhakeerya. Na Mariko woosi, omwaana waane mubhwiikirirya, arabhakeerya.  
\v 14 Mubhakeerye abhiikirirya bhoosi kwo obhuseegi bhwa Krisito.\f + \fr 5:14 \fk Mubhakeerye abhiikirirya bhoosi kwo obhuseegi bhwa Krisito \ft ku Kiyunaani ni \fqa Mukeerenie kwo okwiihuumbata kwo obhuseegi. \ft Okwiihuumbata kwo obhuseegi, ni tuubho yo obhukeerya ye Ekiyahudi.\f* 
\p Abhiikirirya bha Krisito, omureembe gubhe hamwe neemwe.